  <brief_title>Antimicrobial Resistance of Bacteria in Burn Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analyzing the Antimicrobial Resistance Profile of Bacterial Isolates Obtained From Severely Burned Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
