  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the resistance of pathogenic bacteria in infected
      tissues of burn patients to various antimicrobials and enzyme debriders.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Bacteria that is present in infected burn wounds will be isolated and identified. The
      isolates will be tested for resistance to commercially available antimicrobials.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
